title: Help 52 Savage get some teeth
itunes:title: Help 52 Savage get some teeth
description:
Friday 10/20 - Today on the show we had good friend Maino come by the show where he spoke about his new projects, body count on a female and more. Also, we had a man that goes by the name 52 Savage who is 53 year old inspiring rapper, but don't let that distract you from the fact that he also has no teeth, which is the very reason why there is an go fund me for him to purchase some good old dentures. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a man that left his three year old outside 3 am in the morning, and now she has gone missing.
